data.description: Lovely, well maintained home on a 2 acre tract in Decatur ISD. This home is 2395 sq with 4 large bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms both with double sinks. Gorgeous stained concrete floors, stained knotty alder cabinets, granite countertops, with a split bedroom floor plan. Large primary bedroom and bathroom with a claw foot tub, separate shower, double sink, and large walk in closet. Utility room with tons of cabinet space and an under mount sink. 3 spacious guest bedrooms and guest bathroom with double sinks. Covered back patio great for entertaining. Oversized 3 car garage with side entry and concrete driveway. Newly fenced backyard and RV cover. Professional pics will be added Friday.
